      "data": {
        "description": "Create feature branch, empty commit, draft PR",
        "prompt": "Create a new feature branch from the current branch, make an empty initial commit, and create a draft pull request. Use conventional branch naming based on the task description.",
        "model": "sonnet",
        "outputPorts": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "task-analyze-1",
      "type": "subAgent",
      "name": "task-analyze-1",
      "position": {
        "x": 700,
        "y": 600
      },
      "data": {
        "description": "Understand requirements and decompose into domain tasks",
        "prompt": "Phase 1 - Task Understanding: Read and analyze all relevant project documentation to understand the requirements, architecture, and constraints. Review CLAUDE.md, design documents, and any referenced specification files to build comprehensive context for the task.\n\nPhase 2 - Task Decomposition: Decompose the task into subtasks and determine which domains (Frontend, Backend, Infrastructure, Design) need work. If only one domain is affected, route to that domain's solo branch. If multiple domains are affected, route to the default branch for parallel execution across all domains.\n\nFor Backend tasks, also determine whether the target service uses Haskell (svc-bff, svc-data-collector, svc-portfolio-planner, svc-risk-guard, svc-execution, svc-audit-log) or Python (svc-signal-generator, svc-feature-engineering).",
        "model": "opus",
        "outputPorts": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "domain-switch-1",
      "type": "switch",
      "name": "domain-switch-1",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": 600
      },
      "data": {
        "evaluationTarget": "Task decomposition routing result: which domains need work",
        "branches": [
          {
            "label": "Frontend",
            "condition": "Only frontend changes needed"
          },
          {
            "label": "Backend",
            "condition": "Only backend changes needed"
          },
          {
            "label": "Infrastructure",
            "condition": "Only infrastructure changes needed"
          },
          {
            "label": "Design",
            "condition": "Only design changes needed"
          },
          {
            "label": "default",
            "condition": "Other cases",
            "isDefault": true
          }
        ],
        "outputPorts": 5
      }
    },
